# ── LLM Providers ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# The chat API tries providers in this order: Groq → OpenRouter → Cerebras
# Add at least ONE key. Groq is recommended (fastest, generous free tier).

# 1. Groq  –  https://console.groq.com/keys
GROQ_API_KEY=gsk_...

# 2. OpenRouter  –  https://openrouter.ai/keys
OPENROUTER_API_KEY=sk-or-...

# 3. Cerebras  –  https://cloud.cerebras.ai
CEREBRAS_API_KEY=csk-...
